target.message: Changes to analysis subprocess, possibly from when we were trying to get multiprocess analysis working?

Removed testing code.
Removed unfinished feature that let you set shots as inactive.
Removed unused imports.

Stamped as version 2.0.0 for release.

Closed Qt branch ready for merge.

Added ability to clear all points of interest

Note that there is currently a bug/undesired feature where selecting the zoom or pan tool will not uncheck the add/remove points tools. Need to look into intercepting the signal or modifying the functions called by these tools.
